<p><strong>Tiny undead, neutral evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 13</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 40 (9d4+18)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 0 ft., fly 40 ft. It can hover.</p>

